{"tid":1589131,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【fb轉載】護目鏡推介連Link","createTime":"2019-09-23T06:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T15:09:03.000Z","uid":306582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9088977f93b8bb99a732867448b4eb66cfbbb9e7","tid":1589131,"uid":306582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:46:28.000Z","msg":"以下由fb copy and paste過嚟<br />\n<br />\n原po: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104035790996146/posts/110594150340310?substory_index=0&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104035790996146%2Fposts%2F110594150340310%3Fsubstory_index%3D0%26sfns%3Dmo&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK69qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=47fed380\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104035790996146/posts/110594150340310?substory_index=0&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Zdc8XL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Zdc8XL.jpg&h=faef7f6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[🥽護目鏡推介連Link]<br />\n-<br />\n今次講下發夢點樣保護雙眼，齋氣密嘅選擇唔多講，如果唔係散光嘅手足用泳鏡就99.9%氣密，以下講下啲起碼有MIL-PRF 32432或者STANAG 4296軍事級防撞嘅鏡：<br />\n-<br />\n‼️四眼仔👓首選：ESS Striketeam SJ（圖左上）<br />\n呢款周街斷哂貨，就知係神器啦！全氣密，海棉邊超貼面，最重要係OTG (Over-The-Glass)戴到眼鏡👓！但係呢副連登仔狂推之後周圍都斷哂貨，版主亦問過好多間網店，基本上美國網話In Stock嗰啲你落完單佢都係話要20日lead time🤷🏻&zwj;♀️如果大家見到真。有貨就唔好手軟，即買！<br />\n💲建議零售價：US$50<br />\n💰入手價：約US$40<br />\n↖️ <a href=\"https://www.esseyepro.com/Striketeam-SJ_67_detail.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esseyepro.com%2FStriketeam-SJ_67_detail.html&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK69qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=812a87ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.esseyepro.com/Striketeam-SJ_67_detail.html</a><br />\n-<br />\n🇪🇺歐洲大把貨：Boll&eacute; CHRONOSOFT（圖右上）<br />\n呢款版主都係近期先留意到，好適合🔥火系魔法師，唔單止附合NATO軍事標準，仲可以防百幾度高溫，全氣密。雙層鏡片更加安全同防霧，軟身膠邊實測亞洲面型都好貼。唯一缺點係非OTG，版主覺得應該可以喺膠邊✂️剪開少少位俾鏡框，未必會影響氣密度，不過未實測。<br />\n💰入手價：&pound;30<br />\n↖️ <a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Bolle-Chronosoft-FR-Safety-Goggle/dp/B01DAKXBRA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2FBolle-Chronosoft-FR-Safety-Goggle%2Fdp%2FB01DAKXBRA&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK69qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=ce99fbea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.uk/Bolle-Chronosoft-FR-Safety-Goggle/dp/B01DAKXBRA</a><br />\n-<br />\n🛠加工變氣密：Rothco OTG（圖左下）<br />\n呢副之前唔少人有講過，因為唔氣密所以慢慢被淘汰咗，但其實只需要攞熱溶膠將佢上下四個氣孔封住就ok👌🏼（已實測），重點係超平‼️，仲要香港🇭🇰 @militaryguy 就有得賣，貨期兩個星期左右。<br />\n💰入手價：HK$209<br />\n↖️ <a href=\"https://www.mg-military.com/index.php?route=product/product&amp;product_id=4337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mg-military.com%2Findex.php%3Froute%3Dproduct%2Fproduct%26product_id%3D4337&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK69qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=70d0ec94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mg-military.com/index.php?route=product/product&amp;product_id=4337</a><br />\n-<br />\n❌唔氣密唔好再戴：Uvex Stealth OTG（圖右下）<br />\n發夢成日見到有人戴，唔知係咪加咗工，但其實呢款嘅Indirect Vents比較難加工，而且防撞得最普通嘅ANSI Z87.1+，真係唔啱戴㗎！🙅🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n-<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可 #光復香港時代革命 #香港人加油"},{"pid":"c8b431535f79d3ac90a90f3bb4006e828ac95252","tid":1589131,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"4d2ed9b93242f3846a6775f78231d4b8ce4240ba","tid":1589131,"uid":249960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fceadabbd6ca02adf76b93cba6a3522ee161233b","tid":1589131,"uid":306582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d2ed9b93242f3846a6775f78231d4b8ce4240ba","tid":1589131,"uid":249960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d0a3805e9fb0a71b88ed4cadc895c9a361f169","tid":1589131,"uid":306582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:52:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d8adbc9addcfb5d63b6dfc9644e09ba3bb60ce8","tid":1589131,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:10:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6113a0fa34df8c7842bfef7517fc86b6bf134273","tid":1589131,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"其實唔好見眼會更好，推薦泳鏡"},{"pid":"53837152478ad53fbe077af289beee58c20bc5a1","tid":1589131,"uid":306582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6113a0fa34df8c7842bfef7517fc86b6bf134273","tid":1589131,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"其實唔好見眼會更好，推薦泳鏡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T20:05:44.000Z","msg":"泳鏡唔防彈，而且一般反光面嘅泳鏡透光度好低，夜晚會勁黑，眼罩痴返反光紙都可以唔見眼，可以睇下面新po👇🏼<br />\n<br />\n【fb轉載】反光紙唔好學popo咁淨係痴一半！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592842</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89deb6db21b85f7dc88376a58d974cf5552b42ad","tid":1589131,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:09:03.000Z","msg":"考慮緊chronosoft"}]}